    <S id="063S1">
        <FORM kindOf="original">se Padain kata se Kapayuanan a namaɫaɫaqedi a qinaɫan.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="original">sə padain kata sə kapajuanan a namaʎaʎaqədi a qinaʎan.</PHON>
        <FORM kindOf="standard">se Padain kata se Kapayuanan a namaljaljaqedi a qinaljan.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="standard">sə padain kata sə kapajuanan a namaʎaʎaqədi a qinaʎan.</PHON>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="eng">The people of Padain and Kapayuanan live in villages close to one another.</TRANSL>
