        <PHON kindOf="standard">nu maqaqəʦi nu maqadadaw, ʦamakaja a sə kapajuanan.</PHON>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="eng">When they fight in the daytime, the Kapayuanan people win.</TRANSL>
