    <S id="063S4">
        <FORM kindOf="original">aza sika tjamakaya, pumatsa pi tsungal a se Padain; avanu sivala djemavats nu qezemezemetj a kiqetsi.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="original">aza sika camakaja, pumaʦa pi ʦuŋaɭ a sə padain; avanu sivaɭa ɉəmavaʦ nu qəzəməzəməc a kiqəʦi.</PHON>
        <FORM kindOf="standard">aza sika tjamakaya, pumaca pi cungal a se Padain; avanu sivala djemavac nu qezemezemetj a kiqeci.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="standard">aza sika ʦamakaja, pumaʦa pi ʦuŋaɭ a sə padain; avanu sivaɭa ɉəmavaʦ nu qəzəməzəməʦ a kiqəʦi.</PHON>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="eng">The reason they win is that the Padain people have eyes in their knees, and so they can march out to fight at night.</TRANSL>
